    "updated_at": "2015-04-04T18:56:56Z",
    "body": "This is currently an intentional decision as by using a trait object it will _always_ be opting out of some marker traits. The only real fundamental piece of functionality we wanted to add to `io::Error` was the ability to send it across threads, hence `Send`. That said we can always tweak this, however.\n",
